{"tid":2046782,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[Twitter戰線] 公司注册都要政治審查 仲唔推爆俾國際知？","createTime":"2020-06-01T15:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T15:37:15.000Z","uid":237361,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"acd6b2e9c9f7025180d423b4f9c2aa2aece097ba","tid":2046782,"uid":237361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:37:15.000Z","msg":"發覺晨光萬事屋被公司注册處留難單嘢冇乜人推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係呢單野絕對值得煲大！</span><br />\n<br />\n而家大國角力，香港係國際間最大嘅利用價值就係金融白手套，而呢單嘢就正正顯示出香港嘅營商自由點樣被蠶食！比起乜嘢人權乜嘢民主，外國持份者更加在乎呢樣關乎佢哋利益嘅事！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事件詳情已經有巴打岀過post<br />\n<br />\n［精準打擊］國安法未到， 公司註冊處率先開始審查黃店向港人宣戰！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2045218\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2045218</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我建議大家幫手推Hong Kong Free Press對於呢件事嘅報道，一黎專業媒體報道詳盡，二黎啲英文真係寫得好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hongkongfp/status/1267257780735533056?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongfp%2Fstatus%2F1267257780735533056%3Fs%3D21&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8w9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=fc98f60e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongfp%2Fstatus%2F1267257780735533056%3Fs%3D21&h=fd820c34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hongkongfp/status/1267257780735533056?s=21</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 唔係twitter戰線專家，有冇手足知道可以tag咩人最有效，集思廣益"}]}